# tree-sitter-pgn

## Overview

Chess Portable Game Notation (PGN) grammar for [tree-sitter](https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter).

## Used in

 * [Emacs pygn-mode](https://github.com/dwcoates/pygn-mode)

